            <div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
              <p>Could we add a feature to the table visualization editor that allows the viz to highlight cells that match a certain criteria? Imagine rules for  <code>&gt;</code> <code>&lt;</code> <code>==</code> <code>!=</code>. Perhaps it could even accept multiple rules (yellow for one criteria, red for another etc.)</p>
